sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Commit History Webview
participant Router as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as RewriteSelectedCommitsUseCase
participant Repository as GitRepository
participant Worktree as Worktree
participant Plans as OperationPlanRegistry

User->>App: Squash, fixup, or drop selected commits
App->>Router: rewrite request(repoLocator, worktreeLocator, selectedHashes)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repoLocator)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repository and Worktree
Router->>UseCase: plan(repository, worktree, selectedHashes)
UseCase->>Repository: getReachableCommitHashes(selectedHashes)
alt A selected commit is not reachable
  UseCase-->>Router: validation error
  Router-->>App: history/error(validationFailed)
else Selection is reachable
  UseCase->>Repository: orderCommits(selectedHashes, oldestFirst)
  UseCase->>Worktree: getInteractiveRebasePlan(baseRef, headRef)
  UseCase->>Plans: store guarded rewrite plan
  Router-->>App: guarded operation plan
  User->>App: Acknowledge rewrite
  App->>Router: guarded acknowledgement(planId)
  Router->>Plans: validate acknowledgement
  alt Squash
    Router->>UseCase: execute squash plan
    UseCase->>Worktree: squashCommits(orderedCommits, message)
  else Fixup
    Router->>UseCase: execute fixup plan
    UseCase->>Worktree: fixupCommits(orderedCommits)
  else Drop one commit
    Router->>UseCase: execute drop plan
    UseCase->>Worktree: dropCommit(commit)
  end
  Router-->>App: operation success and refresh requested
end
